  "texts": [
    "We used two data-split approaches for creating training and validation subsets for the single-cell treatment classification task:",
    "Leave plates out: we selected the plates in a way that the data of one subset of plates is only the train data and another one is in validation.",
    "Leave cells out: all plates are used for training and validation.",
    "We randomly choose single cells from each well, meaning that approximately 60% of cells from each well would be in the training set and the rest in the validation set.",
    "The training of deep learning models was performed on NVIDIA DGX with NVIDIA V100 GPUs and servers with NVIDIA A6000 GPUs; a single GPU was used to train each model."
  ],
